data.description: This spacious ranch-style home boasts just under 4,000 square feet with 4 bedrooms, and 2.5 bathrooms. Sitting on a 1.5 acre lot - a rare find within city limits - the property is scattered with mature trees giving a serene and private backyard retreat. The back deck, patio, and gazebo offer plenty of options for enjoying the surroundings, and the all-season sunroom is the perfect spot to take it all in. Inside, you'll find generously sized rooms and plenty of space. The main floor master suite ensures the conveniences of one-level living, while the basement provides many functional options for storage, a workshop, and the potential for more bedrooms and living spaces. The current offerings of this property check a lot of boxes, and there is untapped potential just waiting for a new owner!
